            "html": "<p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">Always say \"Bon jour!\" first thing to any person you encounter, especially if you're hoping that person will help you in any way. And do say it with a pleasant smile on your face.  Also, look out for the \"I just found this wedding ring and I think it belongs to you\" scam. I encountered that one three times in one morning, and several times thereafter.</span></p> ",
